          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "This method causes glyph generation and layout for the line fragment containing the specified glyph, or if noncontiguous layout is not enabled, up to and including that line fragment. If noncontiguous layout is not enabled and "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "effectiveGlyphRange"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " is not "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "NULL"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ", this method additionally causes glyph generation and layout for the entire text container containing the specified glyph."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Overriding this method is not recommended. Any changes to the returned glyph range should be done at the typesetter level."
            }
